{"tid":1475648,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全港罷幫NGOs 賣旗、做義工、做會員","createTime":"2019-08-15T14:22:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T12:51:56.000Z","uid":276921,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0b3debeac262f447b8e25c4411df5f28034dcaa8","tid":1475648,"uid":276921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:22:31.000Z","msg":"小弟P牌，做緊社福界；第一次出Post，屌得細力少少<br />\n<br />\n如題，大家見到社福界成日罷工，以為機構好support同事出去參與運動？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">都痴L線！</span></span><br />\n基本上係逼你自取AL、CL，或者自動幫你 No Pay Leave！<br />\n<br />\n如果中心同事想真 ‧ 罷工？佢會各種威逼你，令你點都有人開門，變相其實無影響！<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">有人話，機構已經好好，你仲想佢點？做咩針對機構？咁都要向funder交代嫁？</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你老味，大是大非，機構高層都係社會上有影響力，你地唔出聲，其實已經另類幫緊淋病！</span>仲要有D中高層口講支持運動，但就叫同事唔好令到機構被label同政治有關，叫同事去遠D派傳單，去遠D幫手做補給；仲有人以為自己比兩個臭錢夾物資就當自己做左野？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你以為買贖罪劵呀？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你以為咁係社會公義呀？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">另類割席咋！</span></span><br />\n所以，真心咪再幫個班無事就叫你賣旗、做義工既社福機構，因為一有事起上黎，佢地只會龜縮，仲會阻住真心想幫拖既社福同工做野。另外，都唔好幫佢地做會員，因為會員條數係同社署有agreement，如果追唔到，機構係要嘔錢補返。反正班高層都唔幫我地，做咩要為佢諗咁多？叫佢食自己啦！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">題外話：<br />\n社福界仲有一大班講就凶狠既社工同老鬼，仍然打緊2014年雨傘既飛機，講到自己幾大contribution，慳D啦！</span></span>"},{"pid":"9959849782a1a0d385a61338994d06afde3b1ff4","tid":1475648,"uid":276921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:27:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"198a80d200524a30221a81bf3fa98bed21cc123e","tid":1475648,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:47:06.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\ni know that feel bro"},{"pid":"01d60670a3b910a6810aec55ec9e6a70d96572b5","tid":1475648,"uid":293282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T19:44:07.000Z","msg":"一人一email俾NGO叫佢地出聲明反對警暴<br />\n<br />\nNGO近年收入:<br />\n1. 宣明會 香港 2018收入：超過9.1億<br />\n2. 無國界醫生（香港） 2017年總收入：超過5億港紙<br />\n3. 樂施會 （香港） 2017總收入：超過2.5億港紙<br />\n4. 奧比斯香港2018年總收入： 超過2.1億港幣<br />\n5. UNICEF HK 2017年總收入：1.7億（個人捐款佔超過7成）<br />\n6. Save the Children (徐子淇喺Ritz Carlton搞ball嗰間）2017香港收入：超過1.6億港紙<br />\n7. 香港紅十字會 2017/18年總收入： 超過1.4億港紙(公眾捐款超過1億港紙)"},{"pid":"ac4c965a08b88c213ee6f40837f3064011e45af4","tid":1475648,"uid":17812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:51:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R6z7q5Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR6z7q5Y.jpg&h=cc2f3dc6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MpTzQxD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMpTzQxD.jpg&h=8a83645e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SD7g3SE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSD7g3SE.jpg&h=c3d87592&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pMxkL50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpMxkL50.jpg&h=712e21f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NGNMGEk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNGNMGEk.jpg&h=be0e5720&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zDmBjq1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzDmBjq1.jpg&h=4071fb3f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nvdj1Em.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnvdj1Em.jpg&h=c91c4ec7&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}